### Team Management
@baseUrl = https://cost-katana-backend.store/api
@apiKey = your_api_key

### Create Team
POST {{baseUrl}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Engineering Team"}

### Add Member
POST {{baseUrl}}/teams/{{teamId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"email": "user@example.com", "role": "developer"}

### List Teams
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
